Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:05.80,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, there was a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:10.40,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The knight never faltered in his duty, no matter what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:15.81,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,He did not even falter in taking the life of his lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:19.05,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what he took pride in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:29.51,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,But the knight could not do anything but carry out his duty,\Nand even after his death, he still seeks a duty to carry out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:33.63,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the knight, who became a\Nghost and now haunts this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:39.36,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,holds in his hand the blood-stained\Nsword that pierced his lover's breast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:10.61,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Wandering Knight"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.02,0:03:14.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he appeared again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You're all spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, nothing's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Come to think of it, today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The day Fakir-sama comes back to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:34.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how wretched he'll look when he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.34,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:38.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're completely a Fakir-sama girl now too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:42.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No, I'm telling you, Fakir and I aren't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:46.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, if you're that serious about it,\NI have to support you, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll support you with all I've got too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:50.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then! First comes the love confession!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They seem kinda freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we shouldn't get involved with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You be careful too, Ahiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:08.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a shrimp, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:16.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're expressing our own inner worlds in concrete form.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:19.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And your image is that of a duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:19.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what division are you a student in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ballet division.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:25.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Might she...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:27.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we ask her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then. Do you know Mytho-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:37.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, we're looking for a boy to\Ndance ballet for us in our play.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:41.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd really love to ask Mytho-sama to do it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.81,0:04:42.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:46.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll give me your beautiful heart, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:48.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, as he is now, Mytho is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, would it be okay if Fakir did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:53.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:58.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He pushes people he doesn't like out the window, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:02.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! And he's just as good at ballet as Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:06.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. With things as they are,\NFakir-senpai would be okay too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:07.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:12.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a copy of the script. Could you\Ngive it to Fakir-senpai for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:26.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're back, Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.43,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I protect Mytho. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:43.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A knight who couldn't even die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:54.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The knight's role in the story was to be torn in two and die,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,but not only were you saved in that unseemly way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,you've got the nerve to STILL be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:02.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the story, you're no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:05.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you'll just be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Fakir. I'm happy to have you here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of play it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you like plays, Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ballet is dancing, but there's stories to it and stuff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:25.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's kind of like a play, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:25.81,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:32.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,See, the people from the Drama Club say they\Nwant you to dance the ballet in their play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So read this script!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:39.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you join clubs and stuff it'll be\Neasier for you to come to school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:44.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stick close to Mytho as much as you can, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:48.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to tell me to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.94,0:06:50.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll leave it to you, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:58.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:06.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad blood between people has a\Nway of eventually going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you doing a club activity? That's excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:16.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys and girls working towards one goal,\Nsweating youthful sweat together...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,As you're doing that, a new meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:22.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually, love blooms! And marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:28.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it is important to be involved\Nin something in a positive manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:30.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:36.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it's possible to turn a\Nlove made impure back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:38.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a difficult issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is an "impure love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:46.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can say that Odile's love is impure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Fakir read the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:06.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Fakir he... I guess he wouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:11.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:12.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir! You came...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the rest of this script?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean "the rest"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It ends in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It does?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:23.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You hadn't even read the script and you dumped it on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:33.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but everyone said the part was perfect for you and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So the ghost knight is perfect for me, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of story is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:46.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hailed as the strongest of knights\Nand enemy nations all feared him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:51.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The knight believed his duty was to\Nrisk his life to protect his king.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:57.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He even killed his own lover, who was a spy\Nfor an enemy kingdom, without faltering.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, the two nations made peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,but the knight was exiled from his\Ncountry in wretched fashion,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:07.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,and from then on, knew not whom to\Nprotect or whom to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He died that way and his soul still\Ncontinues to wander this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The script ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of a sad story, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a funny story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:20.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rue-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:23.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A knight who wanders around unable to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is perfect for you, Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.36,0:09:28.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rue-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Rue-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Ahiru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, Fakir is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My! You really brought him along?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:47.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no record of when it was written or by whom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:58.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to find it while I was cleaning the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:02.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was inside this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:05.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was afterwards that the strange\Nrumors started going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the ghost knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for a story to come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:13.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it makes good advertising for our play, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:18.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I just have to dance the role of that ghost knight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to help us, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.45,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nicer than we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely going to be a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Break a leg, Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:26.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:34.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why does this story bother me so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream I had, what the hell did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:43.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something strange about Fakir.\NI wonder what was wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:50.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He decided to do it! So I can be glad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:55.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I wonder what I can do for Mytho?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:59.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is searching for his heart shards really all I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.99,0:11:03.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's right! You mustn't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that you're not abandoned by the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:09.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So that you're not forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some water, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:46.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the heart? Hurry up and give me a heart to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:52.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to capture a sacrifice in the prince's place, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU did?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What a useless thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:57.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:03.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You will not be loved by anyone, but\Nme and the prince in the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:08.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is NO way you will ever be loved so much\Nthat someone would give their own life for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:11.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:16.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to get in the prince's way again,\Nyou would lose even my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'll do things right this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost knight and this book and the dream I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir, everyone's assembled already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:37.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:45.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I dream about the ghost knight? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:50.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the ghost knight send me that dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:58.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The knight who's lost sight of his place to die,\Nseeking something from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he want me to give him a place to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:06.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, does it mean he'll prepare a place for me to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost scary somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:13.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if he really were the ghost knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:15.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out shopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I think I'd probably be faster. Want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then please buy these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:21.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:25.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I didn't forget anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:29.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it kinda feels like the town's quieter than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:31.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that because of the ghost knight rumors after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:34.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better hurry back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:50.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That was marvelous. This play will definitely be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just like Ahiru-san said, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:54.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Ahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had her go into town to do some shopping for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you do us the honor of formally joining our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Fakir-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably can't hope for much from him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:20.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair is very lovely. It's just like crow's feathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:26.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Well? Have you decided on the next sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:31.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those who possess young and beautiful\Nhearts who are worthy of sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just taking my time deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you getting impatient?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:39.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, there've been some interesting rumors lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the ghost knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know everything, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that from getting your heart back too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princes need strong knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:52.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What if you got the famous ghost knight on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:56.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you can't do anything, Kraehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:15:00.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get angry. It's the truth, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I'll do as you say, Kraehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I getting this bad feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this is that script's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, is this the ghost knight's fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:19.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kinda creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did this town have a forest like this in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a horse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't really such a thing as the ghost knight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:36.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He was real!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:11.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Does this mean the ghost knight just now had...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru! Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:16.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, the ghost knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:25.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And he might have a shard of Mytho's heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:25.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:30.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so I still had a duty I could carry out as a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:33.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir, you don't mean to fight with that knight, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:37.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's seeking the enemy he should fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:37.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:41.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,After I defeat him, you return the heart shard to Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we end up dying on each other's\Nswords, just leave me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:56.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that horse already senses\Nwho should be its master.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:01.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give you an enemy you should defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:07.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sword is seeking blood, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:10.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut down that useless knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:11.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just like the dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you are a true knight, do the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who showed me the\Nend of the story, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:30.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you wish, I'll take this sword...\Nand plunge it through your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,you can finally die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:42.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:10.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:20.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight, Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tutu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, where are you, Tutu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:25.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:40.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.14,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:54.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you swing your\Nsword, your heart won't be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've already realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:19:00.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's not your real heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want so badly that you took your lover's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:13.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't stop fighting even after you've died, you're\Nso sad, you suffer so much, you hold so much hate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:20.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really something more precious than a lover's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:26.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting and give back Mytho's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this and give up your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:33.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm from an enemy kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:36.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not saying this for my kingdom's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:38.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying it because I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:41.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want you to bear any more sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:53.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Your battle is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the feeling of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The shards of Mytho's heart that I\Ngave back are making him suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:15.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the one thing I can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:24.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get all of my feelings back as soon as\NI can, with help from Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:28.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'll go back into the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:33.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense that it's best for pieces of\NMytho's heart to go back inside Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Mytho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:41.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tutu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the ghost knight able to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.80,0:21:15.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir, is it okay if I sleep a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:23.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't my sword even protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:40.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm in a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:47.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Something sinister is going on, but every\Nsingle one of them is totally useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:50.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Edel were here at times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.34,0:21:52.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:29.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want you brandishing a sword. I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:31.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't acknowledge me as a knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:34.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have raven's blood running through\Nyour veins, just like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:37.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have you, I can become a prima ballerina, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:41.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling that's grown to the bursting\Npoint inside you, that's real love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.85,0:23:43.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! What is this "real love"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:45.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're seeking is false love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:49.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If this love is false, then all the love\Nin the world is false love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:55.19,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Midsummer Night's Dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:54.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,All you children who love stories, come gather around.
